<HEADLINE>
<P>
5 FEARED KILLED IN BLAST ABOARD COAL FREIGHTER 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By Reuters 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>
<P>
OSLO 
</P>
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
An explosion on a Norwegian freighter loaded with coal killed two crew members 
and hurled three others into the South Atlantic, the Norwegian Rescue Service 
said Sunday. 
</P>
<P>
The captain and chief officer were among those missing. 
</P>
</TEXT>
