<HEADLINE>
<P>
BETTING WITH JANICE; 
</P>
<P>
THE REMATCH AT OAK TREE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
I closed the week with a $50 loss when Excellent Guest proved rude in the third 
race Sunday. 
</P>
<P>
Janice Goldinger's Sun. Bankroll: $2,232.50 
</P>
<P>
Sunday's Loss: $50 
</P>
<P>
Current Bankroll: $2,182.50 
</P>
<P>
SURELOCK lost $100 when Stylish Star finished fourth in the eighth race. 
However, the computer got back its $60 exacta wager in the ninth when Reppus 
Tuolluf was scratched. 
</P>
<P>
SURELOCK's Sun. Bankroll: $390 
</P>
<P>
Sunday's Loss: $100 
</P>
<P>
Current Bankroll: $290 
</P>
<P>
Note: Janice Goldinger, a horse owner, does not bet on races her horses run in. 
SURELOCK does not own horses. 
</P>
