MINNESOTA TIMBERWOLVES (BASKETBALL TEAM); BASKETBALL PLAYERS; SPORTS 
FRANCHISES; UNIVERSITY OF CALIFORNIA AT IRVINE; CALIFORNIA STATE UNIVERSITY AT 
FULLERTON 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
